The '''Iskalon Effect''' was a giant tidal wave on [[Iskalon/Legends|Iskalon]] in [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]] that destroyed the city of [[Pavillion]]. It was caused by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] who were trying to kill [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]]. It is reported that a [[Merman]] was killed by this event.

